data.description: AMAZING TOWNHOME! 3 Bedrooms | 2.5 Bathrooms | 1 Car Garage w/ double parking pad, located in the highly desirable THE PRESERVE in Odessa, FL.  1st Floor offers Open Concept with Kitchen, Dining, Living Room, and half bathroom.  Spacious Living Room opens onto Covered Screened Lanai, offering additional outdoor entertaining space.  Kitchen has granite center island with breakfast bar seating.  Separate Dining area. 2nd Floor includes the Master Suite with En Suite Bathroom, 2nd & 3rd Bedrooms, 2nd Bathroom, and the Laundry area.  SMART HOME features include touchpad that connects alarm system, keyless access entry, (Skybell) video door bell and other smart devices.  THE PRESERVE offers top notch amenities including Clubhouse w/ Fitness Center, 2 Swimming Pools, Basketball, Dog Park, Playground, Soccer/Sports Field, and direct access from the community onto the Suncoast Trail. BIKE ~ RUN ~ WALK.  Nearby beaches, golf courses, medical facilities, schools, shopping, restaurants, and much more! LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!  Easy access to SR 54, Suncoast Expressway, Tampa airport & downtown Tampa.  Zoned for TOP RATED schools in Pasco County.  *ASK ABOUT THE 2.625% ASSUMABLE FHA MORTGAGE LOAN. *Special Terms & Conditions Apply.
